title: The No Jumper Show Ep. 53
description:
Welcome back to the No Jumper Show. Today Adam22, Camgirl & Housephone are joined by 24K Goldn as the dive into this weeks top stories in hip hop 2:10 Special guest on the show 24K Goldn 4:00 How did 24K Goldn heard about Housephone telling the story on the show 7:09 24K Goldn tells his side of the story of what really happened 19:20 Adam explains why people turn on Tory Lanez besides the obvious reasons 23:20 Kanye uses the mental health for people to not cancel him yet people make fun of Megan 46:00 Housephone tells the story of him and Phonia the great's brother being a fan of the store to now being a super producer on Billboard 47:33 adam’s pokemon go weekend experience with guapdad 49:07 How to maintain your waves while Pumper waves are social distancing 1:09:38 24K Goldn lockin in and working with tik tok producers 1:11:54 Harlow/Smokepurpp and label deals with new artists 1:45:42 Akademiks' mad at Adam for the Sara Molina Interview 1:47:26 24 hours No Jumper stream coming up 1:54:02 6ix9ine deleting his IG has no effect at all on his buzz + skinny fromthe9 getting shot seems fake 2:00:16 young thug told Elliott WIlson he's only doing interviews with No Jumper and a couple other platforms 2:02:11 24K Goldn's crazy fan story who tried to steal his underwear http://www.twitter.com/nojumper http://www.instagram.com/nojumper https://www.facebook.com/No-Jumper-198283650194402/ http://www.reddit.com/r/nojumper FOLLOW CAM GIRL https://instagram.com/camgirl https://twitch.tv/camgirl FOLLOW LIL HOUSE PHONE https://instagram.com/lilhousephone Follow Adam22: http://www.twitter.com/adam22 http://www.instagram.com/adam22 and adam22hoe on Snapchat #NoJumper #Live
